Here's the full info:

  ---
  1. Get All States

  GET /api/locations/states

  Request:
  GET /api/locations/states
  // Optional query param:
  GET /api/locations/states?country_id=101

  Response:
  [
      { "id": 1, "name": "Andhra Pradesh" },
      { "id": 2, "name": "Arunachal Pradesh" },
      { "id": 27, "name": "Maharashtra" },
      ...
  ]

  ---
  2. Register User

  POST /api/register

  Request:
  {
